  <brief_title>To Evaluate Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics, And Food Effect Of Single Doses Of GSK945237 In Healthy Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Two-Part Study to Evaluate Safety, Tolerability, and Pharmacokinetics of Single Escalating Oral Doses of GSK945237 and the Effect of Food on Single Oral Doses of GSK945237 in Healthy Adult Subjects</official_title>
